DESCRIPTION:Are you feeling lost\, overwhelmed or lonely? Do you sometimes 
 feel you are just... a bit tired of being a human? Mother Earth is calling 
 you! Sign up for this unique trans-species experience combining shamanic wi
 sdom and astonishing tree science. You are invited to step beyond human lim
 itations and enter the boundless experience of becoming part of the forest!
  Expect mind-blowing thought experiments\, life-changing silly role plays\,
  and collective rituals that shake your whole being. Disclaimer: Mushrooms 
 are involved—but in completely legal ways. "This performance is weird\, w
 ise\, and wildly original... Imagine if Carl Jung\, Marina Abramović\, and
  your funniest friend went on a mushroom trip together—that’s the terri
 tory we’re in.” --Bespoke Black Book\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.ap
 p/comedy-atlas/event/psytreedelic-xperience/
